      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AWICKED WOMAN (10) put the writing on the wall when runner-up two back then raced wide and was checked but still managed a win at Young when last seen seven weeks ago. Has joined Nathan Turnbull since and was readied with a trial win. Draws for a trail so could kick off for the new yard with a win. SINFUL KISS (3) recorded another strong performance last start when she was third at Dubbo. That made it back-to-back placings having missed by a head prior. Should enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position so could break through. SYDS JOY (4) draws better than when beaten narrowly as runner-up at Young three days ago. Looks close to a win. VINNYSGAL (5) could be ready to deliver after she came from the back row to miss narrowly at Dubbo a week ago.",
